---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
    title="sjrah.net/about"
    description="Learn about Steve Jevon Rahardjo - Data Science graduate from Monash University specializing in backend systems, AI/ML, Python, Go, and database technologies."
    page="about"
>
    <div class="container page">
        <h1 class="page-title">
            <span>About</span>
        </h1>

        <p class="text">
            I am a Computer Science graduate from <strong
                >Monash University Malaysia</strong
            > with a focus on backend systems and AI-centric development.
        </p>

        <p class="text">
            Currently, I am refining several side projects to build a deeper
            understanding of
            <strong>network programming</strong> and <strong
                >database optimization</strong
            >. I also dedicate time to following <strong>LLM research</strong> and
            its practical application in software products.
        </p>

        <p class="text">
            My goal is to apply these technical interests to scalable,
            real-world systems while staying up to date with the evolving AI
            landscape.
        </p>

        <h2 class="section-subtitle">Skills</h2>
        <div class="skills">
            <div class="skill-item">
                <span class="skill-label">Languages</span>
                <span class="skill-value"
                    >Python, Java, Go, SQL, R, TypeScript</span
                >
            </div>
            <div class="skill-item">
                <span class="skill-label">AI/ML</span>
                <span class="skill-value"
                    >LLMs, RAG, Google ADK, Hugging Face, Scikit-Learn, XGBoost</span
                >
            </div>
            <div class="skill-item">
                <span class="skill-label">Data Tools</span>
                <span class="skill-value"
                    >PySpark, Kafka, MongoDB, QdrantDB, Pandas, Matplotlib</span
                >
            </div>
            <div class="skill-item">
                <span class="skill-label">Dev Tools</span>
                <span class="skill-value"
                    >Git, Docker, GitHub Actions, Flask, BeautifulSoup</span
                >
            </div>
        </div>

        <h2 class="section-subtitle">Education</h2>
        <div class="education">
            <div class="education-item">
                <h3 class="education-title">
                    Bachelor of Computer Science (Data Science)
                </h3>
                <p class="education-school">Monash University Malaysia</p>
                <p class="education-year">Feb 2023 — Nov 2025</p>
            </div>

            <h2 class="section-subtitle">Experience</h2>
            <div class="experience">
                <div class="experience-item">
                    <h3 class="experience-title">
                        Data Analyst Trainee (CDP Team)
                    </h3>
                    <p class="experience-company">SynergyXYZ</p>
                    <p class="experience-year">Nov 2024 — Feb 2025</p>
                    <p class="experience-desc">
                        Researched Customer Data Platform vendors, formulated
                        CDP service offerings, and compiled technical
                        documentation. Gained experience with Google Ads.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="experience-item">
                    <h3 class="experience-title">Website Admin (Volunteer)</h3>
                    <p class="experience-company">PPI Monash Malaysia</p>
                    <p class="experience-year">Jul 2024 — Nov 2025</p>
                    <p class="experience-desc">
                        Executed website revamp using WordPress, published
                        content, and assisted in event program coordination.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</BaseLayout>
